The Falling is a 2014 British mystery drama film written and directed by Carol Morley .
It stars Maisie Williams and Florence Pugh as best friends at an all-girls school .
The film also stars Greta Scacchi , Monica Dolan , Maxine Peake , and Mathew Baynton .
Production began in October 2013 .
The film premiered at the BFI London Film Festival on 11 October 2014 and was released theatrically on 24 April 2015 in the UK .
The Falling earned # 468,762 on a # 750,000 budget .